  <h2>Regenerative Medicine Treatments</h2>

  <h3>Platelet-Rich Plasma (PRP) Therapy</h3>
  <p>PRP treatments use your body's own healing factors to promote tissue repair:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Single Joint PRP</strong>: Treatment for one joint or localized area</li>
    <li><strong>Multiple Joint PRP</strong>: Treatment for multiple joints in one session</li>
    <li><strong>Cosmetic PRP</strong>: Facial and aesthetic applications</li>
    <li><strong>Hair Restoration PRP</strong>: Scalp treatments for hair loss</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Exosome Therapy</h3>
  <p>Advanced cellular therapy using exosomes for tissue regeneration:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Joint Injection</strong>: Targeted treatment for joint conditions</li>
    <li><strong>Soft Tissue Injection</strong>: Treatment for muscle and tendon injuries</li>
    <li><strong>IV Exosome Therapy</strong>: Systemic treatment for overall wellness</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Peptide Therapy</h3>
  <p>Customized peptide treatments for various health optimization goals:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Initial Peptide Consultation</strong>: Assessment and protocol development</li>
    <li><strong>Monthly Peptide Supply</strong>: Ongoing peptide therapy</li>
    <li><strong>Peptide Monitoring</strong>: Regular follow-up and adjustments</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>IV Nutritional Therapy</h2>
  <p>Intravenous delivery of essential nutrients and vitamins:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Basic Hydration IV</strong>: Electrolyte and fluid replacement</li>
    <li><strong>Wellness IV</strong>: Comprehensive vitamin and mineral blend</li>
    <li><strong>Performance IV</strong>: Enhanced formula for athletes and active individuals</li>
    <li><strong>Recovery IV</strong>: Post-illness or post-procedure support</li>
    <li><strong>Custom IV Blend</strong>: Personalized nutrient combinations</li>
  </ul>

